sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant Pipeline
    participant LLM
    participant Memory
    participant Executor
    participant Analyzer

    User->>CLI: helixqa autonomous --project . --platforms all
    CLI->>Pipeline: NewSessionPipeline(config, provider, store)
    CLI->>Pipeline: Run(ctx)

    Note over Pipeline: Phase 1: LEARN
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: BuildKnowledgeBase()
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Read docs, code, git, prior sessions
    Pipeline->>Memory: Load prior findings, coverage

    Note over Pipeline: Phase 2: PLAN
    Pipeline->>LLM: Generate test plan from KnowledgeBase
    LLM-->>Pipeline: 30 PlannedTests (JSON)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Reconcile with existing banks
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Rank by priority

    Note over Pipeline: Phase 3: EXECUTE
    Pipeline->>Executor: Start video recording
    loop For each test
        Pipeline->>Executor: Screenshot(ctx)
        Executor-->>Pipeline: PNG bytes
        Pipeline->>Executor: Crash/ANR check
        Pipeline->>Memory: RecordCoverage(screen, platform)
    end
    Pipeline->>Executor: Stop video, collect logcat

    Note over Pipeline: Phase 3.5: CURIOSITY
    loop 5 iterations per platform
        Pipeline->>Executor: Random navigation
        Pipeline->>Executor: Screenshot(ctx)
    end

    Note over Pipeline: Phase 4: ANALYZE
    loop For each screenshot
        Pipeline->>LLM: Vision analysis
        LLM-->>Analyzer: AnalysisFindings (JSON)
    end
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: DetectMemoryLeak()
    Pipeline->>Memory: FindingsBridge.Process()
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Write issue tickets to docs/issues/

    Pipeline-->>CLI: PipelineResult
    CLI->>Pipeline: WriteReport()
    Pipeline-->>User: Session complete
